item.title: Cloudflare Pages
item.description: What is Cloudflare Pages? Cloudflare Pages is a JAMstack platform for deploying static websites. As part of Cloudflare’s suite of web performance and security services, Cloudflare Pages leverages the global Cloudflare network to deliver high-speed, secure, and scalable web experiences.
